{"tid":2316754,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不只有線上演唱會⋯⋯Source Music 將舉行線上選秀會！","createTime":"2020-12-08T05:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T05:53:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bd76aec5780b01ee9c1b7fa578e9c2ae0fa19e23","tid":2316754,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_5bbc93634ca702aea9cefeb21c9c619b/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132170-888042.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_5bbc93634ca702aea9cefeb21c9c619b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132170-888042.png&h=b77a2e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在 GFRIEND 大獲成功後，Source Music 也將繼續尋找新的女團人才，有興趣的少女無論身在哪個國家都能報名參加徵選！<br />\n<br />\nSource Music 本週公開了《2020 SOURCE MUSIC UNTACT GLOBAL AUDITION》的海報，並宣布將從 7 日起至 20 日間徵選未來的韓流女團人才。這是繼今年 5 月後 Source Music 再度舉行的全球選秀活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a29b2c46b58276b83f51c3d98ecf1df2/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132170-888041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a29b2c46b58276b83f51c3d98ecf1df2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132170-888041.jpg&h=4bfdb005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要於 2002 年後出生（含 2002 年）、對 K-Pop 有興趣的少女，無論來自哪個國家都可以報名參加《2020 SOURCE MUSIC UNTACT GLOBAL AUDITION》。由於疫情造成跨國移動不便，這場選秀將報名和徵選全部改為線上進行，更有利於各地少女參加。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，Source Music 成立於 2009 年，並在去年為 Big Hit Entertainment 收購為旗下廠牌，目前旗下僅有 GFRIEND 一組藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6ee1cf44007003a1c36671321a6575c5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132170-888043.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6ee1cf44007003a1c36671321a6575c5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132170-888043.jpg&h=80d01092&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}